136031\" data-attachment-id=\"136031\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_pyre/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2132,1059\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_Pyre\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The cyno is lit capsuleer\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pyre.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136031\"\u003eThe cyno is lit capsuleer\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen each of the leaders went down their list of fallen.  I was a bit surprised when Aragorn spoke, because Halbarad was mentioned as one of the fallen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136032\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136032\" data-attachment-id=\"136032\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_halbaradmemorial/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1828,964\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_HalbaradMemorial\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Halbarad gone for the tale\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=1198 1198w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_halbaradmemorial.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136032\"\u003eHalbarad gone for the tale\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI cannot remember if he ever got to hear how I stuck it to the Falcon Clan leader in the caves at Helm’s Deep.  Some others of the Grey Company perished as well, but Halbarad was Aragorn’s main Lieutenant.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen, I went with Eomer to pay respects to Theodan, who  was lying in state within the city.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136024\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136024\" data-attachment-id=\"136024\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_goodtobetheking/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1413,778\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_GoodToBeTheKing\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Eomer stating the obvious\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_goodtobetheking.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136024\"\u003eEomer stating the obvious\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAfter which it was time for the big planning session, the “what do we do now?” part of the siege, where they acknowledge that Sauron was just going to come at them again and that the only real hope was the destruction of the ring.  As such, they would set out to the black gate with such forces as they could muster to distract Sauron, to make him think that the new master of the ring sought to assail him, to keep Frodo and Sam’s mission from his mind.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136022\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136022\" data-attachment-id=\"136022\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_trapforwho/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1297,719\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_TrapForWho\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Let’s not forget we’re going into a trap as well\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_trapforwho.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136022\"\u003eLet’s not forget we’re going into a trap as well\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat included a lot of dialog lifted straight from the book… which is fine.  It is worthwhile to put quotes into the mouths of people who said them.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd then I was given another list of tasks, a shopping list of supplies and some recruiting and persuasion objectives as the leaders stood around outside the pavilion and smoked and exchanged anecdotes about past times in the city.  Even Gandalf grew bored with that and stood apart from the military leadership wing of the party.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136041\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136041\" data-attachment-id=\"136041\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_pavillionleaders/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2031,1121\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_PavillionLeaders\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Eomer, Aragorn, Tistann, and Imrahil\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_pavillionleaders-1.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136041\"\u003eEomer, Aragorn, Tistann, and Imrahil\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI will say that Aragorn has a pretty fancy bed in that tent.  Did they grab that out of the city or did some poor contingent of the Grey Company have to carry that broken down into pieces all across Middle-earth?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136040\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136040\" data-attachment-id=\"136040\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2860,1340\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_AragornsSleepingChamber\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Aragorn’s sleeping chambers\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_aragornssleepingchamber.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136040\"\u003eAragorn’s sleeping chambers\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI mean, granted, it doesn’t look like he’s slept in it… or used the bath… or read the books on the table… or partook of the smorgasbord of food behind me in that picture… but still, seems pretty sumptuous.  I should be thankful my quest chain didn’t include heating the water for that tub.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnyway, on finally wrapping all of that up, I was sent forward to Osgiliath, the next stop on the journey forward to Mordor.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_136033\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136033\" data-attachment-id=\"136033\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/06/20/on-pelennor-field-after-the-siege/mp28_osgiliath/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2860,1340\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP28_Osgiliath\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Riding across the Pelennor to Osgiliath\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/mp28_osgiliath.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-136033\"\u003eRiding across the Pelennor to Osgiliath\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFinally the destination of the NPCs aligns with my own destination, which is Mordor.  Over the river and through the woods, to Sauron’s house we go.  There are just a few details to take care of along the way… there always are.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
